entry.title: San Diego Python Monthly Meetup January 2023

media:group.media:title: San Diego Python Monthly Meetup January 2023
media:group.media:description:
This is our monthly meetup livestream from January 26, 2023.
Meetup link: https://www.meetup.com/pythonsd/events/290263327/
Thanks for coming to our stream or coming in person. Thanks to Ansir Cowork for having us there. Thanks to Microsoft for providing the snacks, and thanks to JFrog for being awesome and having a cool giveaway!
